Host gitlab.com github.com
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
    PubkeyAuthentication yes

###

Host x1 x1.home
    HostName x1.home
    User alex
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
    PubkeyAuthentication yes

